Lil Wayne Ft. T-Pain & Mack Maine - Got Money (Official Video)
---------------------------------------------------------------

It was shot on June 23 in Los Angeles. The video was filmed on the same day the video for A Milli was shot. The video is a follow up to the cliffhanger of A Milli. The video is directed by Gil Green. The music video is said, by Lil Wayne, to be based on the 2006 film Inside Man. The video will feature Young Money artist Mack Maine. Ray J and Birdman make appearances in the video. The music video premiered on multiple MTV channels on July 28, 2008 at 6 a.m.
